Sorting

Bubble Sort ( ascending)

- compare adjacent elements and swap if first is greater.
- by the end of first iteration, greatest element will be the last item.
- repeat for n-1 items

Selection Sort ( ascending)

- set first element as minimum
- compare with each item in list
- update minimum
- at the end of first iteration, minimum will have lowest value
- swap with position 0
- repeat

Insertion Sort ( ascending)

- pick each item
- compare with all other items, place it at correct position
